CD40L Vaccine in Adenocarcinoma of the Lung@highlight

The purpose of this study is to find out what effects (good and bad) a tumor vaccine (GM.

CD40L) used in combination with Nivolumab will have on participants and their cancer.

 Another purpose of the study is to find out the maximum tolerated dose of nivolumab in combination with GM.

CD40L vaccine.

 Investigators also want to find out if the combination of GM.

CD40L and nivolumab can boost the immune system of participants like you, and how their immune system reacts, both before and after the treatment.

